songs.title: Boss nigga
songs.lyrics:
(Chorus)

Make way for the boss nigga
It’s 20k for the watch nigga
White Benz drop top nigga
We don’t really give a fuck nigga

Two chains on my neck nigga
Yeah she told me I’m a spec nigga
Got gold on my chest nigga
Better double them zeros on the Cheque nigga (2X)

(Verse 1:: Rhymez)
Rhymez
That’s real talk, let the real talk, do my money dance, wearing flip flops, she said she don’t suck, well that’s sucks
Beat that pussy up,  nunchucks
She said I’m a player cause I got game
Shooting at the stars and I got aim, it’s a jungle out here and it’s wild bitch, yeah I’m chilling at the top of the food chain
Going back to back on the track I spazzed had to to do the math cause I skipped my class now I got a stack so she’s on my back like she tryna smash
Hahaha
Make way for the boss nigga, it’s 20k for the watch nigga, white Benz drop top nigga, we don’t really give a fuck nigga

On the low she give me top nigga
I go Freddie on a Barney like a day dreamer
Too fly bag packs made of propellers
Make it rain all summer like a bad weather
